<H3> <TI>   UGTA Official Assassinated in El Harrach 7 April </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    UGTA Official Assassinated in El Harrach 7 April </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0804123594 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1130 
GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0804123594 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Security services reported that Belaid Meziane, 
Algerian General Workers Union [UGTA] national secretary in 
charge of social affairs, was assassinated yesterday near El 
Harrach by an armed group. 
  The statement of the security services pointed out that the 
victim died at Belfort Hospital in El Harrach. [passage omitted 
on funeral arrangements] 

</TEXT>

