<H3> <TI>   Palestinian Arms Caches Near Sidon Raided, Confiscated </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Palestinian Arms Caches Near Sidon Raided, Confiscated </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    `Palestinian Organizations' Caches </H4>

<F P=102> NC0504175094 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 5 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0504175094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] As part of the military establishment's raids on 
various Lebanese regions, a Lebanese Army unit raided caches 
belonging to Palestinian organizations around Sidon. Sixteen 
caches containing light, medium, and heavy weaponry, along with 
a large amount of rockets and ammunition of various calibers, 
were found. The Army unit listed the weapons and began removing 
them. Six truckloads have already been taken, and work 
continues to empty the caches. 

</TEXT>

