<H3> <TI>   Minister Says Some Church Bombers Fled to Israel, Australia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Minister Says Some Church Bombers Fled to Israel, Australia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0104181094 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1630 GMT 1 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0104181094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Concerning the defendants who 
participated in blowing up the Sayyidat al-Najat Church and who 
are abroad, Defense Minister Muhsin Dallul pointed out that the 
defendants currently in custody had made confessions and 
admitted that each participant carried more than three 
passports. He added: We have information that many of them 
fled to the border zone and from there to Israel. From Israel, 
they left for Australia with passports under false names. 
[passage omitted] 

