<H3> <TI>   Peace Agreement With Shining Path </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Peace Agreement With Shining Path </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Fujimori Has Third Guzman Letter </H4>

<F P=102> PY1404155494 Lima Global de Television Network in Spanish 
0130 GMT 14 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY1404155494 </F>
<F P=104>  Lima Global de Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] President Alberto Fujimori announced today he has 
a third letter from Shining Path leader Abimael Guzman, and that 
he will reveal the letter at the appropriate time. Fujimori 
also denied that a letter published in a local magazine is real. 
[begin recording] 
  Fujimori: [Words indistinct] second, I am keeping 
the third letter under lock, in a safe, and no one else knows 
the combination. I therefore don't see how the letter could 
have left my safe. Then [words indistinct] the magazine 
published a letter which is not the third letter. I deny it. 
[passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

