Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1604143094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has 
disseminated a leaflet in the Gaza Strip threatening that if 
Israel harms its offices abroad, it will launch a war on Israeli 
and Jewish targets overseas. 

</TEXT>

