<H3> <TI>   Islamic Group Claims Responsibility for Train Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Islamic Group Claims Responsibility for Train Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1704182794 London MBC Television in Arabic 1800 GMT 17 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1704182794 </F>
<F P=104>  London MBC Television </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The extremist Islamic Group organization has claimed 
responsibility for the attack that targeted a tourist train last 
night as it was passing through al-Nakhilah village in Abu Tij, 
Asyut Governorate, on the way from Aswan to Cairo. 
  The incident did not result in any casualties. The security 
services searched the area surrounding the scene of the incident. 
  This is the ninth attack against trains in the past two 
years 
and the first since last March. 

</TEXT>

