<H3> <TI>   Bomb Explodes Near Janata Dal Meeting Venue In Kashmir </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bomb Explodes Near Janata Dal Meeting Venue In Kashmir </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1804033594 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0245 
GMT 18 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1804033594 </F>
<F P=104>  Delhi All India Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Jammu and Kashmir, a bomb exploded about 100 
meters away from the venue of a public meeting addressed by the 
Janata Dal leader, Mr. George Fernandes, in Doda on Saturday. 
BSF [Border Security Force] sources said no damage was caused 
by the explosion. 

</TEXT>

