<H3> <TI>   More on Explosion at SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA Office </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    More on Explosion at SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA Office </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1204101794 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 12 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> PM1204101794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow IZVESTIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


