<H3> <TI>   Committee Denies Yeoryiadhis' Involvement in Bomb Attacks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Committee Denies Yeoryiadhis' Involvement in Bomb Attacks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1304135094 Nicosia CYPRUS MAIL in English 12 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> NC1304135094 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia CYPRUS MAIL </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


