<H3> <TI>   Two Suspected RAF Vehicles Discovered </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Two Suspected RAF Vehicles Discovered </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1404161194 Hamburg DPA in German 1507 GMT 14 Apr 94 </F>
