<H3> <TI>   ANAP Official Killed in Kirikkale Armed Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    ANAP Official Killed in Kirikkale Armed Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1504070694 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
