<H4>    Shot While Leaving Home </H4>

<F P=102> NC2004100294 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0945 GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2004100294 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 20 Apr (MENA) -- Brigadier General Shirin 
'Ali Fahmi, commander of the security directorate in Asyut, was 
shot dead in the city center this morning. The brigadier 
general was leaving his home for work when unidentified men 
opened fire at him. Conscript Ahmad 'Ali al-Fuli was also killed 
in the shooting. 
  One of the terrorists was seriously injured during the 
shoot-out with the guards. He was transferred to the hospital. 
Conscript 'Amir Ahmad Husayn was also injured in the attack. 
  Commanders of the Asyut security directorate and criminal 
laboratory officials have started investigations into the 
attack. The search for the criminals has already begun. 

