BFN 

  [Text] Mashhad (Khorasan), April 22, IRNA -- Friday prayer 
leader Hojjat ol-Eslam Aba'i was the target of an assassination 
attempt by a terrorist here today. Aba'i, who substitutes as 
Friday prayer leader in this holy city was fired at twice just 
after delivering the sermon and was immediately rushed to the 
hospital where his health condition was reported as 
satisfactory, said a local official to IRNA. 
  The terrorist after his failed attempt tried to kill himself 
when faced with angry reaction from the worshippers chanting 
`Death to Munafiq (hypocrite)'. 
  Law enforcement officers whisked away the culprit who had 
badly injured himself. 

